All kinds of scripts:

 opp_makemake - create makefile for a simulation
 splitvec     - split an output vector file to separate vectors
 splitvec.bat - splitvec's DOS version
 dos2unix     - convert Windows text files to Unix format
 seedtool.cc  - generates seeds for random number generators
 tcl2c.c      - utility for embedding Tcl source into an executable
 replace.c    - MSVC: substitute @something@ variables in makefiles, .bat files

